John Smith (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Smith_(actor) 0 John Smith (born Robert Errol Van Orden, March 6, 1931 - January 25, 1995) was an American actor remembered in particular for his leading roles in two NBC western television series, Cimarron City and Laramie.
